<font style="color:#000000;"> C++ <<  >>   I/O std::cin std::cout</font>

`<font style="color:#000000;"><<</font>`<font style="color:#000000;">  Stream Insertion Operator</font>

`<font style="color:#000000;">>></font>`<font style="color:#000000;">  Stream Extraction Operator</font>

```cpp
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int x, y;

    //  >> 
    cout << "";
    cin >> x >> y;  // 

    //  << 
    cout << "" << x << "  " << y << endl;

    return 0;
}
```
